{"tid":106584,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下彈丸論破果個神座出流係乜水・・・？","createTime":"2017-02-03T18:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T09:34:37.000Z","uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd06ddf3a2ed094e90fabdb62585dbc4a435f89e","tid":106584,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffafbea035bac25f2735901e17dcd29615a18e6","tid":106584,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:16:45.000Z","msg":"真心？"},{"pid":"796f4ac337937586f63f4b7b0fb5f200ee245314","tid":106584,"uid":18968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"第二集男主角"},{"pid":"6962a69b3c6ea7ea0eb4705f2037a41103418003","tid":106584,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"神座出流即係希望峰學園創辦人<br />\n有個計劃叫神座出流計劃目的係製造人工希望即係集所有才能一生<br />\n二代男主就係接受左呢個計劃既人"},{"pid":"22836c2c000e32e3b497e897763f983bb14dff85","tid":106584,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心？</blockquote><br />\n算係真<br />\n我冇玩過冇睇過<br />\n重要人物?"},{"pid":"1eedb788bb1e6c04f0af29cc10a8f94871c3baba","tid":106584,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"人類史上最大最惡的絕望事件 爆發嘅其中一個原因<br />\n原本係希望𡶶校長，而希望峰有個計畫叫神座出流計畫，目的係將平凡人都可以成為咩才能都有嘅天才<br />\n<br />\n而第二部男主角日向創因為太渴望入到希望峰，結果應學園邀請參加左果個計畫，不過果項實驗有副作用，就係會令原本嘅人性冇左，之後動畫都有講<br />\n<br />\n後期第二代入面自願參加新世界程序，同時放左盾子嘅病毒入去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我真心左?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13706efc5620298f118b9f8a4d20b57405ec8ae","tid":106584,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心？</blockquote><br />\n算係真<br />\n我冇玩過冇睇過<br />\n重要人物?</bloc