r />\n佢結局竟然話所有野都係用動畫洗腦搞到啲人殺人"},{"pid":"4be31cc755abbdd2e4b2e141cb0f0e89e4ecd830","tid":106584,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實彈丸論破玩D梗會唔會太多?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第6集笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得之前播完果時好多人屌個end<br />\n好差咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔差在劇透你彈丸原本玩推理懸疑<br />\n佢結局竟然話所有野都係用動畫洗腦搞到啲人殺人</blockquote><br />\n動畫洗腦? 就咁聽又真係好似幾劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實就咁睇左一集<br />\n套野明顯係狂玩其他作品梗<br />\n但係D觀眾未必明<br />\n所以可能會覺得D對白劇情怪怪地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35a9048c8203ecc6590bd7f449ca81fbb9e291b","tid":106584,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實彈丸論破玩D梗會唔會太多?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第6集笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得之前播完果時好多人屌個end<br />\n好差咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔差在劇透你彈丸原本玩推理懸疑<br />\n佢結局竟然話所有野都係用動畫洗腦搞到啲人殺人</blockquote><br />\n動畫洗腦? 就咁聽又真係好似幾劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實就咁睇左一集<br />\n套野明顯係狂玩其他作品梗<br />\n但係D觀眾未必明<br />\n所以可能會覺得D對白劇情怪怪地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不嬲都係咁唔會唔明，就算唔明啲人咪又覺得好睇<br />\n二代堆人吹到好威話係大boss啲親信，未出三代諗住大boss用啲精彩野傳教，點知三代話睇完條片就跟左大boss"},{"pid":"55b15f77d0749908ff2bac8e575a6bd4e9ad259e","tid":106584,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"BD賣得果3400幾隻<br />\n睇黎動畫真係整得幾劣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}